# ❄️ Cold-Chain Supply OpenEnv

A real-world OpenEnv environment for optimizing **cold-chain vaccine distribution**, focusing on maintaining temperature integrity, minimizing cost, and improving supply efficiency.

---

## 🚀 Project Overview

This environment simulates real-world cold-chain logistics where an AI agent learns to:

- Maintain vaccine temperature stability
- Optimize shipment routing
- Balance cost, waste, and reliability
- Handle supply chain uncertainties

---

